@startuml
title Ownership Split

left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "ecs" as ecs
rectangle "scheduler" as scheduler
rectangle "engine" as engine
rectangle "engine_net" as engine_net
rectangle "engine_net_quic" as quic
rectangle "engine_replay" as replay
rectangle "cavern_hunt" as game

note bottom of ecs
World / Entity / Query / Bundle
end note

note bottom of scheduler
Schedules / labels / execution
end note

note bottom of engine
App / runtime / plugins / bridge
end note

note bottom of engine_net
SimulationTick / protocol /
session / replication contracts
end note

note bottom of quic
Concrete QUIC transport backend
end note

note bottom of replay
Replay / checkpoint substrate
end note

note bottom of game
Concrete game state, snapshots,
patches, replication policy
end note

engine --> ecs
engine --> scheduler
engine --> engine_net
engine --> replay

quic --> engine_net

game --> ecs
game --> engine
game --> engine_net
game --> replay

@enduml